					<mark>In-depth knowledge</mark> of our areas of expertise backed
					up by a proprietary collection of translation memories and termbases.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="human">
				<img
					src="/setapart.svg"
					alt="checked svg"
					loading="lazy"
					decoding="async"
				/>
