					We commit to <mark>100% human translation</mark> to ensure precision,
					cultural fidelity, and contextual accuracy in every project.
					Why? <a
						href="https://www.quora.com/What-are-the-differences-between-machine-translation-and-human-translation-in-terms-of-accuracy-fluency-etc"
						>Read on.</a
